<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, August 18 (Xinhua) -- Defense Minister Igor Sergeyev
said Wednesday that he is confident that the Russian Armed Forces
will eliminate the gangs of Islamic extremists in Daghestan very
shortly.
</P>
<P>
Sergeyev made the statement during a trip to the republic that
