development achievements, saying that Kenya can learn much from
China.
</P>
<P>
J. N. Kimkung, head of a KANU delegation and also Assistant
Minister for Industrial Development, said that China's opening-up
policy and economic reforms are very successful.
</P>
<P>
Kimkung who led the KANU delegation and returned after a China
