<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, August 18 (Xinhua) -- The World Food Program
has extended its five-day food distribution program to displaced
Afghans in Kabul for two more weeks through August 26, a U.N.
spokesman announced Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
