<HEADLINE> Canada Sends Fire Specialists to Turkey </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
OTTAWA, August 19 (Xinhua) -- Canada is sending two hydrocarbon
fire specialists in a first team to help put out the oil refinery
fire in Izmit, Turkey.
</P>
<P>
