At the invitation of Foreign Minister Tang Jiaxuan, Deputy
Prime Minister and Minister of Foreign Affairs and International
Trade Rajkeswur Purryag of Mauritius will pay an official visit to
China from August 23 to 27, 1999.
</P>
<P>
At the invitation of Foreign Minister Tang Jiaxuan, Minister of
Foreign Affairs Vardan Oskanyan of the Republic of Armenia will
pay an official visit to China from August 24 to 29, 1999.
</P>
<P>
Foreign Ministry spokesman Zhu Bangzao made the announcement
here today.
</P>
