<HEADLINE> Nigeria to Retire Officials After 35-year Service </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, August 19 (Xinhua) -- All Nigerian civil servants who
have served for 35 years would be compelled to retire with effect
from the end of this month, reported a Nigerian newspaper
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
