<HEADLINE> World Bank Environmental Protection Loan For Chinese River </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The project will help improve the ecology around the river in
the scenic city of Guilin in the Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region,
according to a report in China Environment News.
</P>
<P>
The project involves sewage treatment, garbage processing, and
water and soil conservation. A sewage treatment and a water and
